OL,4,CRural crime: Bodycams for farmers as
OL,5,Cthey fight rural crime
OL,6, Farmers across Wales are turning to
OL,7, technology to fight rural crime -
OL,8, including wearing bodycams.
OL,10,FA recent survey by NFU Cymru found that
OL,11,F31% of farmers had invested at least
OL,12,F#1,000 in crime prevention measures in
OL,13,Fthe last five years.
OL,15,FIn north Wales, police are working with
OL,16,Fthe farming community to launch Future
OL,17,FFarms Cymru, a scheme using technology
OL,18,Fto tackle thefts on farms.
OL,20,FFarmers will use social media, CCTV and
OL,21,Fbodycams to protect their property.
